<plot>Two lovebirds, Chris and Mimi, joyfully return to Chris's home where Mimi presents a gift to Chris, which he discovers is an inflatable bunny. He later inflates the bunny, and to his surprise, comes to life and wants to be his best friend. The bunny reveals that his name is Mr. Snugglesworth, and the two go out and have a good time. As time passes, though, Chris learns that Mr. Snugglesworth can be a very possessive friend, especially when Mimi turns the duo into a trio.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?061739</url></doc>
